import { CDNURL } from '@vmo/web/constants/config';

const BASE_STATIC_ICON_URL = `${CDNURL()}/static/icons`;

interface ImagesInterface {
  [key: string]: string;
}

const images: ImagesInterface = {

  //2011-xmas

  missionBG:`${BASE_STATIC_URL}/mission_bgm.png`,
